{
  "stem": "20711.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were taught by my parents-- don't brag about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Please don't mention your cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they may feel jealous, you receiving present on Christmastime and they don't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it would hurt them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So don't say it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was almost like a little family secret.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we celebrated practically all the holidays.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember when the springtime-- I think it was on Passover-- when my mother changed dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had beautiful porcelain in attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she would bring it down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And everything became so festive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But in the same time, the Christmas was just as festive for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So, it just show you, you can put the two together in peace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Every evening, we were taught to say the Hebrew evening prayer and also the Catholic-- my mother teached us how to say how God bless my parents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we would include all the Jewish cousins and aunts and uncles into our Catholic prayer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So it-- it didn't cause no conflict.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I never felt-- matter of fact, it-- I felt I belonged to both community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When I was with the Jewish group, I was so thoroughly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But when I went to my Catholic grandmother, I felt like I belonged to that group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I never felt conflict.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But that's-- many people ask me previously about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it certainly didn't happen to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We only spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I never even knew my father is fluent in Yiddish, till I was at least eight years old.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, my father answered the phone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started to spoke a language I never heard before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could hardly wait for her-- for him to put down the phone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, Dad, what did you talk?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
